OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBollywood film accused of  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftrivialising Holocaust     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Jewish organisation has written to   
OL,6, Amazon Prime asking the streaming      
OL,7, service to remove Bollywood film Bawaal
OL,8, from its platform for its "insensitive 
OL,9, portrayal" of the Holocaust.           
OL,11,FThe Simon Wiesenthal Center says the   
OL,12,Ffilm trivialises the "suffering and    
OL,13,Fsystematic murder of millions".        
OL,15,FMany in India have also criticised the 
OL,16,Ffilm for the way it has used the       
OL,17,FHolocaust in the romantic drama.       
OL,19,FBut the cast and director have called  
OL,20,Fthe criticism unwarranted.             
